# Argus — Cursor context pointer

This is Argus, an agentic QA framework (Claude authors/generates/triages/self-heals Playwright
tests; ships as an MCP server + CLI; gated in GitHub Actions).

Before doing anything, read these in order:
1. AGENTS.md            — fast orientation, conventions, commands
2. docs/STATUS.md       — current state, what's done, what's next, how to resume
3. docs/DESIGN.md       — architecture and the rationale behind every decision
4. docs/ROADMAP.md      — milestones M0–M4 mapped to Linear tickets TRE-22..45

Key conventions: TypeScript + ESM, pnpm workspaces, tsup build, Vitest, ESLint flat config.
Verify with: pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck && pnpm test && pnpm build. Never claim done without
running them. Current next task: TRE-30 (the sample-shop Next.js app).
